Maintainer: Remy Drouilhet <remy.drouilhet@imag.fr>
BugReports: remy.drouilhet@imag.fr
Description: Computes the probability for a standard Brownian motion to stay in a wedge of the plane limited by two straight lines, given by their slopes and intercepts.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), Rcpp (>= 0.9.10)
